Subject: [PATCH 4/7] ASoC: dt-bindings: qcom,sm8250: Add SM8475 sndcard

Add SM8475 sndcard using SM8450 sndcard const. SM8475 changes consist of only modifying this binding, so that a different firmware folder is used instead.
---
 Documentation/devicetree/bindings/sound/qcom,sm8250.yaml | 1 +
 1 file changed, 1 insertion(+)

diff --git a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/sound/qcom,sm8250.yaml b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/sound/qcom,sm8250.yaml
index dae440ecab59..8c650a9f7f9c 100644
--- a/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/sound/qcom,sm8250.yaml
+++ b/Documentation/devicetree/bindings/sound/qcom,sm8250.yaml
@@ -25,6 +25,7 @@ properties:
           - enum:
               - qcom,eliza-sndcard
               - qcom,kaanapali-sndcard
+              - qcom,sm8475-sndcard
               - qcom,sm8550-sndcard
               - qcom,sm8650-sndcard
               - qcom,sm8750-sndcard
